Component.Description:
Represents Controller Data and properties that can be used to facilitate input.

@param buttonState The current state of the buttons being pressed represented by integer bits
@param changedButtons Which buttons (represented by integer bits) have been changed (pressed or
unpressed)
@param isActive Whether the controller is active or not
@param type What type of controller it is: 0->controller 1->hand
@param directTouchEnabled Whether direct touch is enabled or not
@param directTouchButtonState The state of the direct touch buttons
@param laserEnabled Whether the laser is enabled or not
